{"title":"别","date":"2019-11-17T04:52:20.000Z","date_formatted":{"ll":"Nov 17, 2019","L":"11/17/2019","MM-DD":"11-17"},"thumbnail":"https://i.loli.net/2019/12/30/Y48Rj3kIgnomOBU.jpg","link":"2019/11/17/别","comments":true,"tags":["诗"],"updated":"2020-12-14T15:10:11.497Z","content":"<blockquote><p>黎明到黄昏，终点就是起点。</p>\n<footer><strong>——佐伊</strong></footer></blockquote>\n<span id=\"more\"></span>\n<p>我从日暮醒来<br>\n黑夜，无尽，寂静<br>\n混沌的思绪<br>\n涣散的情恸</p>\n<p>长夜将尽<br>\n随手拾回几个残片<br>\n松软而咸涩</p>\n<p>我伴初阳睡去<br>\n金霞，须臾，寂静<br>\n无言的话语<br>\n虚无的抚慰</p>\n<p>晨曦愈烈<br>\n回首告别每个故人<br>\n微凉而清冽</p>\n","prev":{"title":"献给每一个清晨","link":"2019/11/19/献给每一个清晨"},"next":{"title":"光","link":"2019/11/10/光"},"plink":"http://wardzhou.art/2019/11/17/别/","reward":true,"copyright":{"author":"Birch","license":"Attribution-NonCommercial-NoDerivatives 4.0 International(<a href=\"https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc-nd/4.0/\" rel=\\\"external nofollow\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\">CC BY-NC-ND 4.0</a>)","updated":"December 14, 2020"},"reading_time":"91 words in 1 min"}